arguments.content:
Hawaii Packing List

Based on Emma Johnson's Hawaii Vacation (June 10th - June 20th, 2024)

Essential Items:
- Swimwear (multiple sets recommended for beach days and water activities)
- Sunscreen (high SPF, water-resistant)
- Hiking gear (comfortable shoes, lightweight clothing, hat)
- Casual outfits (t-shirts, shorts, sundresses)
- Camera (with extra batteries and memory cards)
- Travel documents (ID, flight tickets, hotel reservations)

Additional Recommended Items:
- Snorkeling gear (for Hanauma Bay on June 12)
- Hiking backpack (for Diamond Head hike on June 13)
- Water bottle (reusable)
- Light rain jacket (for unexpected showers)
- Beach towel
- Sunglasses
- Hat or cap for sun protection
- Sandals/flip-flops
- Dressy casual outfit (for the luau on June 16)
- Small first aid kit
- Insect repellent
- Reusable shopping bag (for shopping at Ala Moana Center on June 19)
- Phone charger and adapters
